Package: pve-snapshot-api
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pve-cluster, zfsutils-linux
Description: Per-volume ZFS snapshot API for Proxmox VE
 HTTP service providing direct ZFS snapshot, clone, and volume
 operations for Proxmox VE nodes. Designed as a systemd daemon
 with PVE API token authentication and cluster-aware request proxying.
